#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.76"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.76:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.76:0.2"
msgid "8. Yodhājīvavagga"
msgstr "8. Warriors"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: dutiyayodhājīvūpamasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.76:0.3"
msgid "76. Dutiyayodhājīvasutta"
msgstr "76. Warriors (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.94"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.76:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, yodhājīvā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, these five warriors are found in the world."

msgctxt "an5.76:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.76:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco yodhājīvo asicammaṃ gahetvā dhanukalāpaṃ sannayhitvā "
"viyūḷhaṃ saṅgāmaṃ otarati."
msgstr ""
"Firstly, one warrior dons his sword and shield, fastens his bow and arrows, "
"and plunges into the thick of battle."

msgctxt "an5.76:1.4"
msgid "So tasmiṃ saṅgāme ussahati vāyamati."
msgstr "He strives and struggles in the battle,"

msgctxt "an5.76:1.5"
msgid "Tamenaṃ ussahantaṃ vāyamantaṃ pare hananti pariyāpādenti."
msgstr "but his foes kill him and finish him off."

msgctxt "an5.76:1.6"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo hoti."
msgstr "Some warriors are like that."

msgctxt "an5.76:1.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo yodhājīvo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "This is the first warrior found in the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.76:2.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo asicammaṃ gahetvā dhanukalāpaṃ "
"sannayhitvā viyūḷhaṃ saṅgāmaṃ otarati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, one warrior dons his sword and shield, fastens his bow and "
"arrows, and plunges into the thick of battle."

msgctxt "an5.76:2.2"
msgid "So tasmiṃ saṅgāme ussahati vāyamati."
msgstr "He strives and struggles in the battle,"

#. VAR: upalikkhanti → upalikhanti (mr)
msgctxt "an5.76:2.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ ussahantaṃ vāyamantaṃ pare upalikkhanti, tamenaṃ apanenti;"
msgstr "but his foes wound him."

msgctxt "an5.76:2.4"
msgid "apanetvā ñātakānaṃ nenti."
msgstr "He’s carried off and taken to his relatives,"

msgctxt "an5.76:2.5"
msgid "So ñātakehi nīyamāno appatvāva ñātake antarāmagge kālaṃ karoti."
msgstr "but he dies on the road before he reaches them."

msgctxt "an5.76:2.6"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo hoti."
msgstr "Some warriors are like that."

msgctxt "an5.76:2.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo yodhājīvo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "This is the second warrior found in the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.76:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo asicammaṃ gahetvā dhanukalāpaṃ "
"sannayhitvā viyūḷhaṃ saṅgāmaṃ otarati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, one warrior dons his sword and shield, fastens his bow and "
"arrows, and plunges into the thick of battle."

msgctxt "an5.76:3.2"
msgid "So tasmiṃ saṅgāme ussahati vāyamati."
msgstr "He strives and struggles in the battle,"

msgctxt "an5.76:3.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ ussahantaṃ vāyamantaṃ pare upalikkhanti, tamenaṃ apanenti;"
msgstr "but his foes wound him."

msgctxt "an5.76:3.4"
msgid "apanetvā ñātakānaṃ nenti."
msgstr "He’s carried off and taken to his relatives,"

msgctxt "an5.76:3.5"
msgid "Tamenaṃ ñātakā upaṭṭhahanti paricaranti."
msgstr "who nurse him and care for him."

msgctxt "an5.76:3.6"
msgid ""
"So ñātakehi upaṭṭhahiyamāno paricariyamāno teneva ābādhena kālaṃ karoti."
msgstr "But he dies of his injuries while in their care."

msgctxt "an5.76:3.7"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo hoti."
msgstr "Some warriors are like that."

msgctxt "an5.76:3.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo yodhājīvo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "This is the third warrior found in the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.76:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo asicammaṃ gahetvā dhanukalāpaṃ "
"sannayhitvā viyūḷhaṃ saṅgāmaṃ otarati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, one warrior dons his sword and shield, fastens his bow and "
"arrows, and plunges into the thick of battle."

msgctxt "an5.76:4.2"
msgid "So tasmiṃ saṅgāme ussahati vāyamati."
msgstr "He strives and struggles in the battle,"

msgctxt "an5.76:4.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ ussahantaṃ vāyamantaṃ pare upalikkhanti, tamenaṃ apanenti;"
msgstr "but his foes wound him."

msgctxt "an5.76:4.4"
msgid "apanetvā ñātakānaṃ nenti."
msgstr "He’s carried off and taken to his relatives,"

msgctxt "an5.76:4.5"
msgid "Tamenaṃ ñātakā upaṭṭhahanti paricaranti."
msgstr "who nurse him and care for him."

msgctxt "an5.76:4.6"
msgid "So ñātakehi upaṭṭhahiyamāno paricariyamāno vuṭṭhāti tamhā ābādhā."
msgstr "And while in their care, he recovers from his injuries."

msgctxt "an5.76:4.7"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo hoti."
msgstr "Some warriors are like that."

msgctxt "an5.76:4.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho yodhājīvo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "This is the fourth warrior found in the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.95"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.76:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo asicammaṃ gahetvā dhanukalāpaṃ "
"sannayhitvā viyūḷhaṃ saṅgāmaṃ otarati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, one warrior dons his sword and shield, fastens his bow and "
"arrows, and plunges into the thick of battle."

msgctxt "an5.76:5.2"
msgid ""
"So taṃ saṅgāmaṃ abhivijinitvā vijitasaṅgāmo tameva saṅgāmasīsaṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr "He wins victory in battle, establishing himself as foremost in battle."

msgctxt "an5.76:5.3"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco yodhājīvo hoti."
msgstr "Some warriors are like that."

msgctxt "an5.76:5.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo yodhājīvo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "This is the fifth warrior found in the world."

msgctxt "an5.76:5.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca yodhājīvā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "These are the five warriors found in the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: pañcime → pañca (bj)
msgctxt "an5.76:6.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcime yodhājīvūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā "
"bhikkhūsu."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, these five people similar to warriors are found among the "
"monks."

msgctxt "an5.76:6.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.76:6.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ gāmaṃ vā nigamaṃ vā upanissāya viharati."
msgstr "Firstly, a mendicant lives supported by a town or village."

msgctxt "an5.76:6.4"
msgid ""
"So pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya tameva gāmaṃ vā nigamaṃ vā "
"piṇḍāya pavisati arakkhiteneva kāyena arakkhitāya vācāya arakkhitena cittena "
"anupaṭṭhitāya satiyā asaṃvutehi indriyehi."
msgstr ""
"He robes up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, enters a village "
"or town for alms without guarding body, speech, and mind, without "
"establishing mindfulness, and without restraining the sense faculties."

msgctxt "an5.76:6.5"
msgid "So tattha passati mātugāmaṃ dunnivatthaṃ vā duppārutaṃ vā."
msgstr "There he sees a female scantily clad, with revealing clothes."

msgctxt "an5.76:6.6"
msgid ""
"Tassa taṃ mātugāmaṃ disvā dunnivatthaṃ vā duppārutaṃ vā rāgo cittaṃ "
"anuddhaṃseti."
msgstr "Lust infects his mind,"

msgctxt "an5.76:6.7"
msgid ""
"So rāgānuddhaṃsitena cittena sikkhaṃ apaccakkhāya dubbalyaṃ anāvikatvā "
"methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevati."
msgstr ""
"and, without rejecting the training and declaring his inability to continue, "
"he has sex."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.76:7.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, yodhājīvo asicammaṃ gahetvā dhanukalāpaṃ "
"sannayhitvā viyūḷhaṃ saṅgāmaṃ otarati, so tasmiṃ saṅgāme ussahati vāyamati, "
"tamenaṃ ussahantaṃ vāyamantaṃ pare hananti pariyāpādenti; tathūpamāhaṃ, "
"bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi. Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco puggalo "
"hoti."
msgstr ""
"I say that this person is like the warrior who is killed and finished off by "
"his foes. Some people are like that."

msgctxt "an5.76:7.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo yodhājīvūpamo puggalo santo saṃvijjamāno bhikkhūsu."
msgstr "This is the first person similar to a warrior found among the monks."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.96"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.76:8.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aññataraṃ gāmaṃ vā nigamaṃ vā upanissāya "
"viharati."
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant lives supported by a town or village."

msgctxt "an5.76:8.2"
msgid ""
